snippet.title: Amber Heard Marks Baby Girl's 6-Month Milestone w/ Rare Pic
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is celebrating half a year of motherhood! On Friday, the "Aquaman" actress' daughter Oonagh Paige officially reached six months of life, and her proud mom celebrated the milestone with a sweet Instagram tribute. Amber shared a photo where she's grinning ear to ear while holding her baby girl on her knees. "The six best months of my life, the first six months of hers," she captioned the shot.
